  "remarks": "\nOleg Anatolyevich Matveychev is a deputy in the State Duma of the Russian Federation and vocal supporter of the Government of Russia in Russian media. In articles and interviews he has promoted policies or actions which destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
